│ 458 /// in the vectorized loop. There is no need to vectorize the cast - the same                                                                                                                              │
│ 459 /// value can be used for both the phi and casts in the vector loop.                                                                                                                                       │
│ 460 static void removeRedundantInductionCasts(VPlan &Plan) {                                                                                                                                                   │
